Package gg.sep.alyx.plugin.storage

Class AbstractJsonObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • gg.sep.alyx.plugin.storage.AbstractJsonObject
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    JsonSerializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AlyxConfig, BotConfig, BotEntry, NoOpPluginData
    public abstract class AbstractJsonObject
extends java.lang.Object
implements JsonSerializable
    A base class for representing Json-serializable models used throughout Alyx. Implements all of the necessary type adapters for subclasses, and implements the JsonSerializable.toJson() and JsonSerializable.toPrettyJson() methods at a basic level.
